## Link to this section训练#

在 COCO8 数据集上以图像大小 640 训练 YOLO26n 100 个 [epochs](https://www.ultralytics.com/glossary/epoch)。有关可用参数的完整列表，请参阅 [Configuration](/zh/usage/cfg) 页面。

示例
    
    
    from ultralytics import YOLO
    
    # Load a model
    model = YOLO("yolo26n.yaml")  # build a new model from YAML
    model = YOLO("yolo26n.pt")  # load a pretrained model (recommended for training)
    model = YOLO("yolo26n.yaml").load("yolo26n.pt")  # build from YAML and transfer weights
    
    # Train the model
    results = model.train(data="coco8.yaml", epochs=100, imgsz=640)

See full `train` mode details in the [Train](/zh/modes/train) page. Detection models can also be trained on cloud GPUs through [Ultralytics Platform](https://platform.ultralytics.com).

### Link to this section数据集格式#

YOLO 检测数据集格式可在 [Dataset Guide](/zh/datasets/detect) 中找到详细信息。要将你现有的其他格式（如 COCO 等）数据集转换为 YOLO 格式，请使用 Ultralytics 的 [JSON2YOLO](https://github.com/ultralytics/JSON2YOLO) 工具。你也可以使用 AI 辅助标注工具直接在 [Ultralytics Platform](https://platform.ultralytics.com) 上标注和管理检测数据集。

## Link to this section验证#

在 COCO8 数据集上验证已训练 YOLO26n 模型的 [accuracy](https://www.ultralytics.com/glossary/accuracy)。无需参数，因为 `model` 会保留其训练 `data` 和参数作为模型属性。

示例
    
    
    from ultralytics import YOLO
    
    # Load a model
    model = YOLO("yolo26n.pt")  # load an official model
    model = YOLO("path/to/best.pt")  # load a custom model
    
    # Validate the model
    metrics = model.val()  # no arguments needed, dataset and settings remembered
    metrics.box.map  # map50-95
    metrics.box.map50  # map50
    metrics.box.map75  # map75
    metrics.box.maps  # a list containing mAP50-95 for each category
    metrics.box.image_metrics  # per-image metrics dictionary with precision, recall, F1, TP, FP, and FN

## Link to this section预测#

使用训练好的 YOLO26n 模型在图像上运行预测。

示例
    
    
    from ultralytics import YOLO
    
    # Load a model
    model = YOLO("yolo26n.pt")  # load an official model
    model = YOLO("path/to/best.pt")  # load a custom model
    
    # Predict with the model
    results = model("https://ultralytics.com/images/bus.jpg")  # predict on an image
    
    # Access the results
    for result in results:
        xywh = result.boxes.xywh  # center-x, center-y, width, height
        xywhn = result.boxes.xywhn  # normalized
        xyxy = result.boxes.xyxy  # top-left-x, top-left-y, bottom-right-x, bottom-right-y
        xyxyn = result.boxes.xyxyn  # normalized
        names = [result.names[cls.item()] for cls in result.boxes.cls.int()]  # class name of each box
        confs = result.boxes.conf  # confidence score of each box

See full `predict` mode details in the [Predict](/zh/modes/predict) page.

### Link to this section结果输出#

目标检测为每张图像返回一个 `Results` 对象。主要预测字段是 `result.boxes`，其中包含每个检测到对象的框坐标、类别 ID 和置信度分数。

属性| 类型| 形状| 描述  
---|---|---|---  
`result.boxes`| `Boxes`| `(N)`| 检测框。  
`result.boxes.data`| `torch.float32`| `(N,6/7)`| 原始 `[x1,y1,x2,y2,conf,cls]`，外加可选的追踪 ID。  
`result.boxes.xyxy`| `torch.float32`| `(N,4)`| `xyxy` 像素框。  
`result.boxes.conf`| `torch.float32`| `(N,)`| 置信度得分。  
`result.boxes.cls`| `torch.float32`| `(N,)`| 类别 ID；转换为 `int` 即可获取名称。  
  
关于各项任务中特定于任务的 `Results` 字段，请参阅[按任务划分的预测结果 (Predict Results by Task)](/zh/modes/predict#results-by-task) 部分。

## Link to this section导出#

将 YOLO26n 模型导出为 ONNX、CoreML 等其他格式。

示例
    
    
